<td colspan="2"><div class="parent"><a rel="nofollow" onclick="return forumCtrl_ctl00_MessageBoard.SwitchMessage(null,5763598);" href="/Messages/5763598/Problem"><img src="https://codeproject.freetls.fastly.net/App_Themes/CodeProject/Img/arrow-up24.png" title="Go to Parent"  style="width:16px;height:16px;border:0" /></a></div>What do you mean by it does not work? The demo does not work or the code copied to your application does not work? There are some pointers below to help you troubleshoot.<br />

<ul>
<li>The <code>IWinToastHandler</code> derived object has to be alive (meaning in scope) when the toast is shown.</li><li>Is <code>CoInitialize()</code> called?</li><li>Is there any error MessageBox shown?</li><li>Is the image path points to a valid image?</li><li>I believe this toast cannot work in a windows service which is in Session 0.</li></ul>
<br />
Hope it helps. Looking forward to your reply.<br /></td>
